{"id": "ChIJ3TUUBAC5woARyM5TOmJ1P3M", "rating": 5, "userRatingCount": 202, "displayName": {"text": "Fleurs et Sel | Bakery", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ3TUUBAC5woARyM5TOmJ1P3M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sVWFUbGZTR2htT0ZGRmFWQmxRVzluTkZBMWRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This bakery is all that and some. I got the chocolate chip cookie with sea salt and brownie fudge noir extreme. The taste of the chocolate chip cookies with sea salt will melt in your mouth! The taste of these cookies is one of the best I’ve tasted in a long time!! My cookie was large full of chocolate chips and was so moist with a sprinkle of see salt. The brownie is massive and also delicious and moist. This is a cashless establishment and only two customers at a time. The decor of the bakery is a French flair. Parking is limited and be ready to stand in line for these delicious pastries. It is well worth it!! Be sure to sign up for the rewards program! ✌🏽❤️💛❤️💛", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This bakery is all that and some. I got the chocolate chip cookie with sea salt and brownie fudge noir extreme. The taste of the chocolate chip cookies with sea salt will melt in your mouth! The taste of these cookies is one of the best I’ve tasted in a long time!! My cookie was large full of chocolate chips and was so moist with a sprinkle of see salt. The brownie is massive and also delicious and moist. This is a cashless establishment and only two customers at a time. The decor of the bakery is a French flair. Parking is limited and be ready to stand in line for these delicious pastries. It is well worth it!! Be sure to sign up for the rewards program! ✌🏽❤️💛❤️💛", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Marian Grant", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101422969954048831240/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtSOrtTA5OF8o96VUhm6LX-O4ykHYZfoKPv-t84YPRIocG0VfcIQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-28T00:38:41.698401279Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sVWFUbGZTR2htT0ZGRmFWQmxRVzluTkZBMWRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sVWFUbGZTR2htT0ZGRmFWQmxRVzluTkZBMWRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b900041435dd:0x733f75623a53cec8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3TUUBAC5woARyM5TOmJ1P3M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ONGNtTmhZV05YV0RsVU9HaDJaV2R5YWs5a1ZFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Without a doubt, the best cookies I’ve ever had.\n\nI drove from San Diego specifically to stock up,  and it was absolutely worth the trip. These are truly world-class desserts. Lara, the owner and baker, is wonderful, and her care and craftsmanship are evident in every detail. If you value exceptional food and believe in supporting passionate, independent entrepreneurs, this place is well worth seeking out", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Without a doubt, the best cookies I’ve ever had.\n\nI drove from San Diego specifically to stock up,  and it was absolutely worth the trip. These are truly world-class desserts. Lara, the owner and baker, is wonderful, and her care and craftsmanship are evident in every detail. If you value exceptional food and believe in supporting passionate, independent entrepreneurs, this place is well worth seeking out", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chris Taylor", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113077828006555311435/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7ePn_AD1WW17ng_CZuOkfVKIttpdP8P4yc_I4kgy6Qov0lNs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-30T00:54:37.034094269Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ONGNtTmhZV05YV0RsVU9HaDJaV2R5YWs5a1ZFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ONGNtTmhZV05YV0RsVU9HaDJaV2R5YWs5a1ZFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b900041435dd:0x733f75623a53cec8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3TUUBAC5woARyM5TOmJ1P3M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4V1dYWlBkMnByU2pWQ1pYVjBVa3BEYTBjNU5tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "What a wonderful gem on West Adams! Lara’s fresh homemade cookies are absolutely delicious\nyou can truly taste the quality, passion, and love in every bite. Beyond the amazing cookies, Lara herself is incredibly warm, welcoming, and professional. She makes every customer feel special the moment they walk in.\n\nAs a French person myself, it was such a pleasure to discover that she speaks fluent French beautifully  a rare and lovely surprise in Los Angeles! Her kindness, positive energy, and attention to detail create such a charming experience.\n\nIf you are in Mid City or West Adams, do yourself a favor and stop by. Exceptional homemade cookies, wonderful service, and an owner with a beautiful heart. Highly recommended! 😋", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "What a wonderful gem on West Adams! Lara’s fresh homemade cookies are absolutely delicious\nyou can truly taste the quality, passion, and love in every bite. Beyond the amazing cookies, Lara herself is incredibly warm, welcoming, and professional. She makes every customer feel special the moment they walk in.\n\nAs a French person myself, it was such a pleasure to discover that she speaks fluent French beautifully  a rare and lovely surprise in Los Angeles! Her kindness, positive energy, and attention to detail create such a charming experience.\n\nIf you are in Mid City or West Adams, do yourself a favor and stop by. Exceptional homemade cookies, wonderful service, and an owner with a beautiful heart. Highly recommended! 😋", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christophe christian", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105030268064257193504/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgAuSrNaamK_OhTyhMNnU8u5Th-GMXy1S5oT3DtBdsb-6Li66g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-27T20:50:18.084176506Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4V1dYWlBkMnByU2pWQ1pYVjBVa3BEYTBjNU5tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4V1dYWlBkMnByU2pWQ1pYVjBVa3BEYTBjNU5tYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b900041435dd:0x733f75623a53cec8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3TUUBAC5woARyM5TOmJ1P3M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oUlgwTkNYekJ4TkVkdWVXUjRTekJTV1dGS01sRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Photogenic and a crowd-pleaser with the sizable delicious cookie. This is something you'd take to impress or show love to whomever is lucky to have this.\n\nThe inside is cozy and modern display of the array of cookie choices. If you have any allergies, don't be afraid to ask or even look it up on their website. The baker/lady behind the counter is very sweet and cheery!\n\nWe ordered 6 cookies: Signature Matcha Chocolat Noir, Signature Nutella Framboise, J'adore S'mores, Cookier Au Beurre Cookie Butter,  Signature Peanut Butter Nutella Chocolate\n\nJust one cookie is very filling so it's not something to take lightly. So far we really enjoyed the the S'mores and Cookie Au Beurre Cookie Butter especially dipping it in milk.\n\nRestroom? No\n\nParking? Yes; If you can't find parking on Cohrans Street or on the same as where Fleur et Sel is located at, then I would recommend to park across the Adams road, it is 1 hour free parking 8am-6pm except Sunday.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Photogenic and a crowd-pleaser with the sizable delicious cookie. This is something you'd take to impress or show love to whomever is lucky to have this.\n\nThe inside is cozy and modern display of the array of cookie choices. If you have any allergies, don't be afraid to ask or even look it up on their website. The baker/lady behind the counter is very sweet and cheery!\n\nWe ordered 6 cookies: Signature Matcha Chocolat Noir, Signature Nutella Framboise, J'adore S'mores, Cookier Au Beurre Cookie Butter,  Signature Peanut Butter Nutella Chocolate\n\nJust one cookie is very filling so it's not something to take lightly. So far we really enjoyed the the S'mores and Cookie Au Beurre Cookie Butter especially dipping it in milk.\n\nRestroom? No\n\nParking? Yes; If you can't find parking on Cohrans Street or on the same as where Fleur et Sel is located at, then I would recommend to park across the Adams road, it is 1 hour free parking 8am-6pm except Sunday.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sheri R", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116279285226832335226/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzB7HtmCRNqfgAAMdptIdXQ4KKFemFM6BrRO3TXf6_UWyjbQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-28T23:29:25.457262671Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oUlgwTkNYekJ4TkVkdWVXUjRTekJTV1dGS01sRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oUlgwTkNYekJ4TkVkdWVXUjRTekJTV1dGS01sRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b900041435dd:0x733f75623a53cec8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3TUUBAC5woARyM5TOmJ1P3M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sRFlrdERiR3RXVlMxbVVteHRZalpSWlRsYVNFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "10/10 can’t recommend this enough. Best cookies I’ve had anywhere in the world, run by the most welcoming and delightful woman! The quality can be tasted, prepared with so much skill and love. Pre order or get here early she sells out every day I’ve seen!! Worth any wait and drive- a must have. We came back 2 days in a row just so wonderful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "10/10 can’t recommend this enough. Best cookies I’ve had anywhere in the world, run by the most welcoming and delightful woman! The quality can be tasted, prepared with so much skill and love. Pre order or get here early she sells out every day I’ve seen!! Worth any wait and drive- a must have. We came back 2 days in a row just so wonderful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "May F", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111474062842024567561/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdAhB2DAzEIdbiCz5Kt_QHDC7Zxn55QGHEfjuEF5g-gJdp_dzZ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-21T15:29:18.908906877Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sRFlrdERiR3RXVlMxbVVteHRZalpSWlRsYVNFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sRFlrdERiR3RXVlMxbVVteHRZalpSWlRsYVNFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b900041435dd:0x733f75623a53cec8"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ3TUUBAC5woARyM5TOmJ1P3M/photos/AWCwydh1STSodXSg3kHPdymqfMXqRYdZG5ySnqOL7qLTv2jL5h98fCuOCx1eqXpRdZzKDARXw0DFW7AYW3Y622EgQQ97ERF93_0PsgtjAfUmU7bT28mBsNiDGg06lCRt8XHV2P0HpNU-AkSgkwL16nMnP3vPx3a5Spg9DLcVfHWcvo92cZ0D8rSdqnHXnwxoTPYNUc8_agUtW1r2RBp8IqbfB0FgyW3jYayiyVRkPAhHU8I-gSfMFgTdrm3yxQhyfSCLrRKpGU4UGp1aSiwYEFVA_JwZNuQSwT_SWt9FNsogIGDGKJ0iK2TYR7hCOKiPzgOpw_4Q9yC6Du7oD9CSN_djiTbhWzWWE28sxikf4ypXlI-6vBg5R-9Dewb4wONFEZSrcWvgal4EblGDMPgBGslwjDhC8R1aKWflCznufe5yEiYoIR5h0msnDZkCPFEWI_-x", "widthPx": 3600, "heightPx": 4800, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Marian Grant", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/101422969954048831240", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtSOrtTA5OF8o96VUhm6LX-O4ykHYZfoKPv-t84YPRIocG0VfcIQ=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "http